ComicInfo.Title: Blown Away; Stalking The Wild Asparagus; Rudely Interrupted; Sex
ComicInfo.Summary:
Blown Away: A mysterious off-screen voice warns a cat-boy that getting oral sex from a cat-girl is not a good idea.
Stalking The Wild Asparagus: Katrina, the odd member of a tribe of jungle cat-girls, tries to convince her fellow tribeswomen of the dietary advantages of asparagus.
Rudely Interrupted: Nikki and Skyler's separate romantic interludes keep getting interrupted by their jobs.
Sex: Laura relates her various sexual liaisons since her change to The Mink to a willing audience in Melody.
